{
"cn"
:
"为 Spec Kit 设计的增强模块，帮助用户快速安装并使用其核心组件 Specify CLI（命令：specify）。\nSpec Kit 是一个用于规范驱动开发（Spec-Driven Development）的工具，它可以引导开发者和 AI 工具规范化 “需求→计划→任务→实现” 的流程。\n这套方法旨在消除“感觉式编程”带来的不确定性，确保开发过程的每一步都紧扣最初设定的目标，从而实现高度可预测、高质量的产出。\n"
,
"en"
:
"An enhancement module for Spec Kit, designed to help users quickly install and use its core component, the Specify CLI (command: specify).\nSpec Kit is a tool for Spec-Driven Development that guides developers and AI tools to standardize the 'requirement → plan → task → implementation' workflow.\nThis methodology aims to eliminate the uncertainty of 'gut-feeling programming,' ensuring that every step of the development process is tightly aligned with the initial goals, thereby achieving highly predictable, high-quality outcomes.\n"
}
